703918f-a.title: Brooklyn: Cumberland Street - Flushing Avenue
703918f-a.text:
Cumberland Street, east side, north from No. 37, seen in the foreground,
is just south of Flushing Ave. Upon the vacant lot once stood the
Boughton farmhouse.
April, 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
